(14, 'Autoencoder', 'Deep Learning', 'Autoencoder is a type of neural network architecture that is trained to copy its input to its output.', 'Dimensionality reduction, feature learning, etc.'),
(15, 'Principal Component Analysis', 'Unsupervised Learning', 'Principal Component Analysis (PCA) is a dimensionality reduction technique that is commonly used to reduce the dimensionality of large datasets while preserving as much variance as possible.', 'Data visualization, noise reduction, etc.'),
